Name: Approved
Description: Approved/Valid dispute that does not need to be paid

Name: WriteOff
Description: An ARDoc that should have been paid but is Uncollectable

Name: Closed
Description: An ARDoc that has been fully paid off

Name: Reversal
Description: An ARDoc that was reversed (either payment or memo write off)

Name: Void
Description: An ARDoc that should have been paid but is Uncollectable
